			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    *<b>Everlore's Recipes for Ogre Blacksmithing</B>*</b></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><A href="mailto:Hondo@obsidian-tech.com">Korupter (E-Marr)</a> | 
		            11/13/2000 10:17:12 AM</b></font></p>
		         <a href="guides.asp">
		         <font face="verdana" size="2">Return to guide listing.</font></a>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2"><p><font face="Verdana"><b>Everlore's Recipes for Ogre Blacksmithing</b></font></p> 
<p><font face="Verdana" size="2">I made this chart with as much accuracy as possible. I
hope every Ogre Blacksmith likes and can find this chart useful to them. I appreciate all the help I received from users. If there is any information that is
incorrect or needs updating please feel free to contact me at this address <a href="mailto:Hondo@obsidian-tech.com">Korupter_(E-Marr)</a>.</font></p> 
<ul>
  <li> <b><font face="Verdana"><a href="http://www.everlore.com/guides.asp?ID=259466">Everlore's
    Guide to General Blacksmithing</a></font></b></li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p align="center"><b><font face="Verdana"><u>Everlore's Chart for Blacksmithing</u></font></b></p>

<table border="1" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td width="100%"colspan="3">
      <p align="center"><font size="6" face="Martel">Ogre Blacksmithing</font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="11%"><b><font face="Verdana">Skill:</font></b></td>
    <td width="21%"><b><font face="Verdana">(Armor) Makes:</font></b></td>
    <td width="68%"><b><font face="Verdana">Ingredients:</font></b></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="11%"><font face="Verdana" size="2">N/A</font></td>
    <td width="21%"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Ogre War Plate Breastplate</font></td>
    <td width="68%"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Adamantite Chain Jointing, Blood
      Temper, Leather Padding, Smithing Hammer, Large Plate Breastplate Mold,
      (3) Folded Sheets of Adamantite</font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="11%"><font face="Verdana" size="2">N/A</font></td>
    <td width="21%"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Ogre War Plate Collar</font></td>
    <td width="68%"><font face="Verdana" size="2">Adamantite Chain Jointing, Blood
      Temper, Leather Padding, Smithing Hammer, Large Plate Collar Mold, (1)
      Folded Sheets of Adamantite</font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
